DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260312T150000Z
UID:698b98413cc3e0c9ecb86dbc@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Week 2\n: Job interview Preparation – Mock Interview\nLearn 
 about the best practices in preparing for the interview including how to l
 eave a strong impression through appropriate body language\, appearance\, 
 handshakes and more.\nThis program is part of a Job Seekers & Keepers seri
 es delivered by Woodgreen Community Services.
LOCATION:Fort York\, Program Room\, Ground Floor
URL:https://tpl.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/698b98413cc3e0c9ecb86dbc
X-SOURCE:Volunteer Toronto
END:VEVENT
